WEBVTT

00:00.893 --> 00:03.365
Excuse me, could you tell me what time it is?

00:03.912 --> 00:04.815
Oh, sure.

00:05.020 --> 00:06.318
It's half past 4.

00:06.800 --> 00:07.471
Oh, great!

00:07.603 --> 00:08.396
It is not late.

00:08.559 --> 00:09.868
One more cup of tea, please.

00:10.267 --> 00:11.199
All right, madam.

00:11.739 --> 00:12.443
Thank you very much.

00:12.977 --> 00:13.989
You're welcome.

00:16.311 --> 00:17.657
What time is the meeting, Jenny?

00:18.462 --> 00:19.634
It's at 5 o'clock.

00:20.649 --> 00:21.715
What time is it now?

00:22.289 --> 00:23.624
It's quarter past 5.

00:24.129 --> 00:25.308
Oh no! I'm late!

